Paid Search & Marketplace
Find customers, drive purchases
Connexity’s Search & Marketplace solutions get you in front of the right customer at the right time. Reach active shoppers making buying decisions.
We’ll efficiently manage your presence within major search engines such as Google & Bing—maximizing the performance of your PLAs, SEM and SEO.
Connexity’s Marketplace program connects you with customers in retail content environments—distributing your product listings to our network of publishers across the web.
More 







Bizrate Insights & Ratings
Let your customer inspire you
Survey your customers to measure their satisfaction, find what causes abandonment, and how your competition compares.
Improve your brand reputation and grow customer loyalty with consumer ratings and reviews syndicated to the top search engines.
More 







Display Media
Connect your brand to your audience
Activate your audience through our programmatic media buying platform or reach in-market shoppers on rich retail environments like Bizrate, Shopzilla, and Beso.
 
Our audience activation platform studies the products consumers buy,  the sites they visit, as well as audience attributes like demographics—giving us valuable insights to connect with your audience.
More 







Why Connexity
Knowledge, systems and experience to grow your business
We’ve connected brands and retailers to consumers for over 15 years. Connexity converts our understanding of in-market shopping behavior into results for our clients.
We’ve built an integrated technology platform that synthesizes our proprietary data and helps our partners learn from, discover, and target their customers.
But we don’t just rely on technology. Our clients can count on dedicated, experienced teams to deliver outstanding service. The results: campaigns that are easier to execute and more effective at hitting tough performance goals.
Together, our integrated technology, quality retail data and premier service set us apart.
More 




















































